  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n1) copy a seed phrase\r\n2) focus the first input field on the seed phrase form\r\n3) CTRL+V  paste the seedphrase, which results in every field being populated\r\n\r\nIf the seed phrase is longer than available inputs, we should also auto switch to the correct number of inputs to match the seed phrase.\r\n\r\nPlaces to implement:\r\n\r\n1. when doing onboarding (i am new to status , I already use status)\r\n2. when importing a wallet account with seed phrase (12 and 24 words options)",
