    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Perhaps if the seed phrase that is copied is exactly 12, 18 or 24 words, paste the seed phrase from the beginning field, irrespective of which field is focused at the moment the user presses CTRL+V?\r\n\r\nAlso the implementation should be tolerant of seed phrase words being separated by:\r\n- single spaces\r\n- multiple spaces\r\n- comma, followed by a space\r\n- carriage returns\r\n- spaces followed by carriage returns\r\n\r\nIf the seed phrase words are separated by any of the things mentioned above, this functionality should still work.\r\n\r\nIn terms of \"Places to implement\", I think this should be implemented everywhere the seed phrase entry control is used (e.g. there shouldn't be any instances anywhere in the app where the seed phrase entry control is used and this functionality isn't supported). ",
